description: Special issue published with Walalla n. 54.
name: Raquel
GN

volume.name: Spider-Man/Dr. Strange: "The Way to Dusty Death"
Untold Tales of Spider-Man: Strange Encounters

description: Iron Man does battle with a hyper-intelligent space probe bent on terraforming the planet! And Tony battles Titanium Man while fielding calls for Stark International! All this and more in this all-new, all-action, all-black-and-white one-shot in the spirit of the Mighty Marvel Magazines of yore, but ALL-NOW in style! The Iron Mania never lets up for a moment over these four stories by some of Marvel’s hottest writers!
name: Berserker; Multitasking; Brainchild; It's Raining Tony

description: "'Herr Wagner, here, started out in the circus before becoming the top second-story man in Europe. "'And don’t let Comrade Rasputin’s size fool you. It’s his artistic talent the Bolsheviks want to ship him to Siberia for—an expert forger of artworks and official documents. "'And Ororo’s skills at thievery are so renowned, even at her delicate age, that she is literally worshipped by the footpads of Cairo, if you can believe it. "'These are my all-new, all-different X Men,' Professor Xavier said."
name: Mark Of Cain Part Three

description: What begins as a quiet nighttime vigil on a rooftop in the Haight-Ashbury for our dreadlocked Eco-warrior soon turns into a night of terror. Drew McIntosh encounters the infamous, Gryphon the Hunter, a ruthless poacher who profits from the illegal animal trade. It's inevitable: Drew and Gryphon are set to clash in the ultimate showdown between hunter and prey.
name: BEGINNINGS

description: Selena, Derrick and Clint have set their sights on London. Selena has survived one war with The Infected but can she make it through a second time? They’ve got a machete that’s hacked its share of infected and a gun with only nine bullets. Ammo, and time, is running out…

Fabletown's favorite superspy Cinderella and her Arabian ally are closer than ever to finding the source of the illicit magics. Meanwhile, at Cindy's store, the new magical shoes are a runaway success – literally!
name: Part Four: Suffragette City

description: Travis Morgan, this was your life! McBane's documentary causes Travis to reflect on a life spent in the practice of war… but the resurrected Dark Lord waits at the end of memory lane, and he's launching an all-out attack on Shamballah! Did somebody just say "fire-breathing dragons"? All we hear is blood-curdling screams.
name: The Once And Future Warlord

description:
The deadline is his eighteenth birthday... After transferring to a new school, Yuuki, a disaster-attracting young student, is told that he is actually the reincarnation of Momotaro from Japanese folklore. What's worse, he was cursed by demons in his previous life! And if he doesn't break the curse, he will die on the day he turns eighteen. Luckily for Yuuki he won't have to battle these demons alone--his three mystical minions, Yukishiro, Masahiko and Sawa will be there to instruct and protect him every step of the way!

Chapter Titles

  • Chapter 1: The Demons and the Awakening of the Blood, Part 1
  • Chapter 2: The Demons and the Awakening of the Blood, Part 2
  • Chapter 3: The Guardians and the Encounter, Part 1
  • Chapter 4: The Guardians and the Encounter, Part 2
  • Chapter 5: Students and Quarrels
  • Bonus Chapter
name: Vol. 1

description: A vacation to the beach turns into more training of Yuki's physical skills. But he gets more than just muscle. In his last day, his sense of 'Sight' from his past life awakens, along with the core of his weapon, the Kibi Dango. Is this clue that Yuki has been looking for?
name: Vol. 2

description: Something old, something new, something velvet, something blue...Shocked and heartbroken when her beloved older sister announces that she's pregnant and getting married to (in Ageha's mind) the most boring man alive, Ageha stumbles onto the job of a lifetime--helping to make her sister's wedding dress. Velvet Blue Rose is a super-exclusive bridal design shop run by Yukari and Mitsuya, two super-hot guys. When Mitsuya, the pattern-maker at V.B. Rose, hurts his hand, will Ageha jump in to save her sister's happy dream of marriage, in spite of her own reservations? Frills and fancy fill this blissful new series from the creator of I Hate You More Than Anyone and Tears of a Lamb!
name: Vol. 1

description: It's a mad dash to get to the church on time for Ageha and Yukari, bearing Hibari's just-finished bridal gown! Ageha will give it her all in the final race to make her older sister's special day as fabulous as possible, but will it be enough? And after the ceremony is over, won't her time with V.B. Rose be over as well?
name: Vol. 2

description: It's summer vacation, and Ageha is looking forward to spending a whole lot more time at V.B. Rose, surrounded by a world of sparkles, getting to know the business, and maybe--just maybe--getting to know Yukari Arisaka better as well. But when Ageha is invited to model a bridal gown in a mock wedding ceremony, who will be her groom?!
name: Vol. 4

description: Finally, Hibari gives birth to a beautiful child and many visitors come to visit her and the newborn at the hospital. Unfortunately, so do Arisaka and Nagare. When they accidentally run into each other, Arisaka's jealousy rears its ugly head once again! Good thing they have Ageha, who's always ready to step in and clear things up for this unruly pair of young lovers...
name: Vol. 5

description: Ageha's meddling may succeed in reuniting the Kuromine siblings, but her effect on the V.B. Rose staff is getting more and more complicated! Her skills as an assistant are growing exponentially, much to the joy of all concerned, and her feelings for Yukari are slowly being noticed by those around her...
name: Vol. 3

description: Arisaka and Kuromine accompany Ageha to visit her best friend Mamoru and her brother, Nagare, at the Hojo High School's Cultural Festival. But the fun gets out of hand as a pair of girls get paint on their uniforms. Good thing for Arisaka and Kuromine, who come to the rescue with their sewing skills! Meanwhile, Nagare continues to play mind games with Ageha and Arisaka as he vies for a chance to win Ageha over. And an unexpected ex-girlfriend enters the scene, stirring up even more trouble! What can all this mean for Ageha and the boys at Velvet Blue Rose?
name: Vol. 6

description: The night of their joint birthday party, Arisaka throws up on Ageha when he accidentally take's a sip of alcohol. Later in the evening as the two sit outside to cool off his buzz, Ageha realizes that Arisaka may have feelings for her, when they accidentally lean into each other for a possible kiss... Sell Sheet Keynote: Pure shojo bliss full of weddings, frills...and hot guys!
name: Vol. 7

description: DIG THIS SCENE! Greedy low-lifes chasing the hard luck charm and $200,000! Meet Drug dealer Dewey Booth, he can't be punished enough! WAILIN'! And what about Rock 'n' Roll loser Wes, he needs money to start his own club. BLING! And then there's Über-stacked Nala, she enjoys humiliating men dumb enough to fall for her. HUSH! HUSH! And let's not forget Vincenze, he gets his kicks from being a jerk! JERK! In the end: deadly FIRES ignite! Heads LITERALLY roll!! And Eyes are SHOT out!!! GULP!
name: HC

description: What happened to Jennifer Havel that turned her into info-terrorist and media-slut Jennie 2.5? Jennie One tells the story as she drops out of art school and builds her socio-political consciousness during one of the most turbulent and violent periods of American history_the passing of the Clean Act and the loss of free speech.
name: OGN

description: Reflecting developments in both MAGOG and JSA ALL-STARS this month, Magog finds himself the odd man out during a massive escape from Haven – and his own team thinks he's somehow responsible for the prison break! Turns out, Magog may have exposed one of the DC Universe's biggest cover-ups! Featuring 56 pages of thrilling JSA adventure from writers Keith Giffen and Matthew Sturges and artist Tom Derenick.
name: Walking Papers

description: Justice League's Vixen joins the fray! Red Tornado has to stop Red Volcano from growing even more powerful and risks losing his human family in the process! And we learn where the other elemental androids' loyalties really lie!
name: Brother Against Brother
